  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t这是aqicn 今日2023.6.27的北京天气与污染报告：<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly9hcWljbi5vcmcvZm9yZWNhc3QvYmVpamluZy8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://aqicn.org/forecast/beijing/\">https://aqicn.org/forecast/beijing/</a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9qUVg1aHBaLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/jQX5hpZ.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/jQX5hpZ.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jQX5hpZ.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n这是共匪“北京气象局”的同一时间天气预报：（共匪从不敢实时预告各城市空气污染情况）<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9Kb2tyTEwwLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/JokrLL0.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/JokrLL0.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JokrLL0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n在此重复一下下面回帖里 “天天吃包子” ID的精彩意见：<b>中国统计有个屁高深啊，不就是睁眼说瞎话吗</b>？<br/>\n<br/>\r\n一个连天气预报都造假胡说的伪政权，空气污染也从不敢预报，很自然。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
